data.description: Seller will consider all reasonable offers!! Introducing this 5.42 acre property with a 2007 built 1,735 sq. ft. outbuilding with room for a motor home and another 30x40 heated shop for your working enjoyment. Bonus is 400 feet of lake frontage on Long Lake Erhard. 3 bed, 3 bath home nestled on a spacious lot. Upon arrival you will be captivated by the serene surrounding of trees. As you step inside the home you will be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan that seamlessly blends the living, dining and kitchen areas. The large primary suite offers stunning views from the deck with a walk in closet and second closet and primary bath. There is an additional main floor bedroom and bath. If you are looking for all the conveniences on one level this is the home as there is also main floor laundry. The lower level has been updated with paint, carpet, interior doors, flooring and new vanity in the full bath. The lake side of the home has a huge entertaining space for all your guests.
